        <characteristic name="Type" typeId="d3f6-19e8-ac9e-ae13">Heavy 1 Template</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="Abilities" typeId="492d-1f80-b777-26f2">When firing the inferno cannon, designate a target unit and place the normal flamer template so that is at least partially over as many unit members as possible. The whole template must be in range and line of sight. Roll to hit once, using the firing model&apos;s BS. If you hit then all models partially or wholly under the template are hit. If you miss, they are each hit on a roll of 4+ instead.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
